شقة في تاون هاوس ماج آي،MAG City،دستركت 7،مدينة محمد بن راشد 79000 درهم - 8862053

Urban Avenue is pleased to offer you this magnificent Brand New studio apartment for rent at MAG City – a new gated community, developed by the MAG Group in Mohammed Bin Rashid City, Dubai.

MAG City gets a prime location in Mohammed Bin Rashid City-Meydan District 7, and it is easily accessible via Al Khail Road. As such, the development lies in proximity to some of the key landmarks in Dubai. Since the project is situated a few distances away from some of the major entertainment and leisure destinations, it is primed to become one of the sought-after residential addresses.  

Property details:
■ Furnished with Brand New Furniture
■ Size: 395 Sq ft
■ Ready to Move In
■ Brand New Studio 
■ Spacious Bright Apartment
■ Modern style open kitchen
■ Has balcony
■ Built-in wardrobes
■ 1 Reserved parking

MAG Eye is designed to deliver an urbane and contemporary lifestyle brimming with all the expected amenities, and combining practicality and affordability. MAG Eye is the door to a whole new experience of sophisticated high-end living in Dubai close to the majestic Burj Khalifa, the Dubai Mall, and in proximity to major business and recreational areas.

Other Features:
■ Solar panel installed for lower service charges
■ Shared Swimming pools
■ Well Equipped Gym
■ Children's play area
■ Easy access to Al Khail Road
■ Close proximity to Meydan racecourse
■ Walk-able community

MAG EYE comprises townhouses and apartments designed by Parsons with meticulous attention to detail. These provide you with elegant living spaces, both contemporary and timeless in their conception. The extraordinary architecture, naturally-lit interiors and sense of refined living make this exceptional gated community a highly desirable place to live.  

Our efforts focus on securing the most profitable property deals for clients of varied income levels at the most strategic locations in Dubai. Urban Avenue Properties; Limitless solutions!
